<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5">
    Selo`s Consonant Chain</font>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=279"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right">
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=279">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=279">
    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is very similuar to the snare line of spells. One advantage of this song is that it can be cast while chasing your opponet. This will allow you to solo very well using special tactics like running around him singing attack songs.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B> Highhold Pass<BR>
<B>Skill:</B> Singing<BR>
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
		<table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
